0.3.2 (master)
  - Second, optional command line argument is checkout dir

0.4.0 (next)
  - Remove old git syntax (backends/rgit.py)
  - Add first argument w/ command, fetch is first supported command
  - Add "manifest" command to write out whatever is checked out now
    in a way that can then be restored from the manifest
  - Add "restore" command that restores from a manifest

Future
  - Feature to report who has made changes since the previous
    checkout or manifest

